009@HistoryLogProps(

030    public DexcomG7CGMHistoryLog() {}
031    public DexcomG7CGMHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int glucoseValueStatusRaw, int cgmDataTypeRaw, int rate, int algorithmStateRaw, int rssi, int currentGlucoseDisplayValue, int egvTimestamp, int egvInfoBitmask, int interval) {
032        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
033        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, glucoseValueStatusRaw, cgmDataTypeRaw, rate, algorithmStateRaw, rssi, currentGlucoseDisplayValue, egvTimestamp, egvInfoBitmask, interval);
034        parse(cargo);
035        
036    }

039        this(0, 0, glucoseValueStatusRaw, cgmDataTypeRaw, rate, algorithmStateRaw, rssi, currentGlucoseDisplayValue, egvTimestamp, egvInfoBitmask, interval);
040    }

064    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
065        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
066        this.cargo = raw;
067        parseBase(raw);
068        this.glucoseValueStatusRaw = Bytes.readShort(raw, 10);
069        this.glucoseValueStatus = getGlucoseValueStatus();
070        this.cgmDataTypeRaw = raw[12];
071        this.cgmDataType = getCgmDataType();
072        this.rate = raw[13];
073        this.algorithmStateRaw = raw[14];
074        this.algorithmState = getAlgorithmState();
075        this.rssi = raw[15];
076        this.currentGlucoseDisplayValue = Bytes.readShort(raw, 16);
077        this.egvTimestamp = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18);
078        this.egvInfoBitmaskRaw = Bytes.readShort(raw, 22);
079        this.egvInfo = getEgvInfo();
080        this.interval = raw[24];
081        
082    }
083
084    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int glucoseValueStatusRaw, int cgmDataTypeRaw, int rate, int algorithmStateRaw, int rssi, int currentGlucoseDisplayValue, int egvTimestamp, int egvInfoBitmask, int interval) {
085        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
086            new byte[]{(byte) 399, 0},
087            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
088            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
089            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(glucoseValueStatusRaw), 
090            new byte[]{ (byte) cgmDataTypeRaw }, 
091            new byte[]{ (byte) rate }, 
092            new byte[]{ (byte) algorithmStateRaw }, 
093            new byte[]{ (byte) rssi }, 
094            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(currentGlucoseDisplayValue), 
095            Bytes.toUint32(egvTimestamp), 
096            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(egvInfoBitmask), 
097            new byte[]{ (byte) interval }));
098    }

103        return cgmDataTypeRaw;

107    }

110    }

112        return algorithmStateRaw;

116    public enum AlgorithmState {
117        WARMUP(2),
118        DEFAULT_ELECTRONICS_WAKEUP(30),
119        DETECTING_DEPLOYMENT(31),
120        REPORTABLE_PERIOD_VALID_EGV(32),
121        REPORTABLE_PERIOD_INVALID_EGV(33),
122        STOPPED_END_OF_SESSION(34),
123        STOPPED_ALG_DETECTED_FAILURE(35),
124        STOPPED_MANUAL_STOP(36),
125        STOPPED_TX_FAILURE(37),
126        STOPPED_SIV_FAILURE(38),
127        STOPPED_ENNVIRONMENTAL_CONDITIONS(39)
128
129        ;
130        private int id;
131        AlgorithmState(int id) {
132            this.id = id;
133        }
134
135        public static AlgorithmState fromId(int id) {
136            for (AlgorithmState r : values()) {
137                if (r.id == id) {
138                    return r;
139                }
140            }
141            return null;
142        }
143
144        public int getId() {
145            return id;
146        }
147    }
